{
  "chapter": "056",
  "title": "陈丞相世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "少时贫困好学",
      "text": "陈<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳武</span>县<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">户牖</span>乡人。少年时家境贫寒，喜好读书，家里有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十亩</span>田，独与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈伯\">伯（陈伯）</span>同住。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈伯\">伯（陈伯）</span>常年耕田，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>外出游学。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>相貌堂堂。有人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"家里这么穷，吃什么能长得这么胖？\"他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫂</span>嫂嫉恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>不过问家中的生产事务，说：\"也不过是吃糠粃罢了。有这样的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">叔</span>子，还不如没有。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈伯\">伯（陈伯）</span>听到这话，就赶走了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇</span>人休了她。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "张负嫁孙女",
      "text": "等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>长大，到了该娶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>的年龄，富贵人家没有肯把女儿嫁给他的，贫贱的人家<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>自己又觉得羞耻。过了很久，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">户牖</span>有个富人叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张负</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张负</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女孙</span>嫁了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>次<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫</span>都死了，没人敢再娶。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>想娶她。邑里有人办丧事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>家贫，就去帮忙，早到晚退以多帮工挣钱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张负</span>在丧事上见到他，只觉得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>仪表不凡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>也因此晚走。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张负\">负（张负）</span>跟着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>到他家，他家住在紧靠外城墙的僻巷里，用破<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">席</span>当门，然而门外却有很多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>来访的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>辙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张负</span>回家后，对他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张仲\">仲（张仲）</span>说：\"我想把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女孙</span>嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仲</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>贫穷又不务正业，全县人都嘲笑他的行为，怎么偏要把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>儿嫁给他？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张负\">负（张负）</span>说：\"哪有像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>这样仪表堂堂的人，会长久<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>呢？\"最终还是把女儿嫁了。因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>穷，就借给他聘礼<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">币</span>帛，又给他办<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>的费用娶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇</span>入门。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张负\">负（张负）</span>告诫<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>女说：\"不要因为他贫穷，就对人不恭敬。侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>伯要像侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲一样，侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫂</span>嫂要像侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲一样。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>娶了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张氏</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>儿后，经济日渐宽裕，交游范围也越来越广。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "分肉均平",
      "text": "乡里举行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社</span>祭，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰</span>，分<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>分得很均匀。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父老</span>们说：\"好啊，陈家这位<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孺子</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰</span>真公平！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>感叹道：\"唉，如果让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>主宰<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，也会像分这<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>一样公平！\""
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "初事魏王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">起</span>兵<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>地，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>攻略<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>交<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>事先已告别<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈伯\">伯（陈伯）</span>，带着一些<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少年</span>前往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span>。他向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王进言而不被采纳，又有人进谗言中伤他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>只好逃走。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "归楚又亡",
      "text": "过了很久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>攻略到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>前去归附，跟随他入关<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，被赐予卿爵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>东归称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>回师平<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span>三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>后东进，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">殷王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信武</span>君，率领原来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的部属，前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打并招<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">殷王</span>，然后凯旋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项悍</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十</span>镒。过了不久，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>大怒，准备<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀当初平〖[定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>国的那些<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将吏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，就把金子和官<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>封好，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者送还给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>，自己独身从小路出走，只带了一把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>。渡河时，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>夫见他是个美<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>独行，怀疑他是逃亡的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>军，腰中必藏有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>，盯着他，想要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>害怕，就解下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服赤身帮忙撑<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>。船夫知道他身上没东西，才作罢。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "归汉受用",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>于是到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">修武</span>投<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军，通过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无知</span>求见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>召他入见。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">万石君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：石奋\">奋（石奋）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中涓</span>，接过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">谒</span>帖，引他入见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>等〖$七人</span>一同进见，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐食</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>说：\"吃完了，就到宾舍去吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>有事而来，所要说的话不能过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span>。\"于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>和他交谈，十分赏识，问道：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军任什么官？\"回答：\"任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。\"当日就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，让他担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">参乘</span>，主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都喧哗起来，说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一日</span>得到一个<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国逃亡的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>，还不了解他的才能高下，就与他同车，还让他来监察我们这些<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>！\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>听到后，更加宠幸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>。于是带他东向<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打败</span>。退兵时，收拢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">散兵</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亚将</span>，隶属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王信，驻军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广武</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "无知辩冤",
      "text": "绛<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌婴</span>等都进谗言诬陷<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>虽然是个美<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>，但如同戴着美<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span>的帽子，里面未必有真货。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>在家时，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫂</span>嫂私通；侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王不为所容，逃归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>；事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>又不合意，又逃归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>尊他为官，让他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>接受<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>钱贿赂，送金多的得好职位，送金少的得差职位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>是个反覆无常的乱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，请<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>明察。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>起了疑心，召来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无知</span>责问。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无知</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所推荐的是才能；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>所问的是品行。如今有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尾生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝己</span>那样的品行却无益于胜负大局，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>哪有闲暇任用他们？<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>汉相争，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>推荐奇谋之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，只看他的计谋是否真能有利于国家罢了。至于私通<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫂</span>嫂、受<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>之类，何足怀疑？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>又召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>责问说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先生</span>侍<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>不合，就去侍<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>又离开，今又来跟着我，讲信义的人本就这样三心二意吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王不能采用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的主张，所以离开去事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>不能信人，他所任用和宠爱的，不是项家人就是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">昆弟</span>，虽有奇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>也不能用，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>这才离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>能任人，所以来归附<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>赤身前来，不收受<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>钱就没有费用。如果<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的谋划有可采纳的，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>就用；如果都不可用，那金钱还在，请封存送回官府，请<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>允许我辞官归故里。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>于是向他道歉，重重赏赐他，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>，统管所有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>从此不敢再说什么。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "反间之计",
      "text": "此后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军猛烈<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span>，切断了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甬道</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城。拖了很久，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>忧虑，请求割让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>以西地区求和。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>不同意。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>纷纷扰扰，何时才能安定？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>这个人，恭敬爱人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人中讲廉<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>、好<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>的多归附他。但到了论功行赏封爵划地时，他又吝啬，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人也因此不依附。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>傲慢少<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>，讲廉<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人不来；然而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>能慷慨赏人爵邑，所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人中那些愚钝嗜利无耻的也多归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。如果两方都能去掉各自的短处，结合各自的长处，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>一指就定。然而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>放纵欺人，不能得到廉<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。但<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军中有可以扰乱的，他<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>那边刚直之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚父</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">锺离眛</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span>等，不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数人</span>而已。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>如果能拿出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万</span>斤<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，行反间之计，离间他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君臣</span>，使他们互相猜疑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>为人猜忌多疑又信谗言，必然会内部相互<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>趁机发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打他，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军就必然成功了。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>认为对，就拿出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>四万斤，交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>，任他随意使用，不追问出入。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "离间亚父",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>既然用大量<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>钱在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军中放出反间之计，散布流言说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">锺离眛</span>等为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>，功劳很大，然而最终不能裂地称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，想与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>联合，以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">消灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项氏</span>而分地称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>果然起疑心，不再信任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">锺离眜</span>等人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>既起疑，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>准备了<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">太牢</span>丰盛的宴席，捧着奉上。一见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者，就假装吃惊说：\"我以为是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚父</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者，原来是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者！\"又把饭菜撤下去，换粗劣的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">草具</span>给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者归来，详细报告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>果然对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚父</span>起了大疑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚父</span>想急攻<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>不信他，不肯听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚父</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>怀疑他，就发怒说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>大局已定，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>自己处置吧！请让我告老归乡！\"还未到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，背上生疽而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>于是趁夜放出〖$二千</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女子</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东门</span>出去，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军追<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>她们，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>就和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>从城<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西门</span>夜里逃出。进入关中，收拢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">散兵</span>再东进。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "伪游云梦擒信",
      "text": "第二年，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者向<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>请命。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>大怒骂人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>踩了他的脚。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>也省悟，于是厚待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张子房</span>最终<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">户牖</span>乡。最终用他的奇计，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">消灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。又常以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>身份随军平〖[定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "伪游云梦",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，有人上书告发<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>说：\"赶紧发兵活<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">埋</span>这小子！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>沉默。又问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>坚决推辞，反问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>是怎么说的？\"皇上如实告知。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"有人上书告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，有知道此事的人吗？\"答：\"没有。\"又问：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>自己知道吗？\"答：\"不知道。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的精兵与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国比怎样？\"皇上说：\"比不过。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>帅有能超过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>的吗？\"皇上说：\"没有人能比。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"如今兵不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>精，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>，却要发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>他，这是逼他作战，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>担忧。\"皇上问：\"那怎么办？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"古代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>时，会见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南方</span>有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦</span>泽，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>假装出游<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦</span>，在陈地会见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。陈，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的西界，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>友好出游，必然无事前来郊迎参见。一参见，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>就可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒</span>住他，这不过是一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">力士</span>就能办到的事。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>认为对，就派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者告知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>在陈会见，说：\"我将南游<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦</span>。\"皇上随后出发。行程还未到陈，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王信</span>果然到郊外迎接道中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>预先备好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">武士</span>，一见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>到，立即<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">捉</span>拿捆绑他，放在后车上。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>高呼：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>已定，我本该被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span>！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>回头对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>说：\"你别出声！你谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，是明摆着的！\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">武士</span>把他反绑。于是在陈会见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，完全平〖[定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地。回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>，又和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>们剖<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>定封。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "户牖侯让功",
      "text": "于是与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>剖<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>，世代相传不绝，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">户牖侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>推辞说：\"这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的功劳。\"皇上说：\"我用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先生</span>的谋划，战胜敌人，不是功劳是什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"如果没有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无知</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>怎能被引进？\"皇上说：\"像你这样可说是不忘本了。\"于是又赏赐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无知</span>。第二年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>身份随军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>地谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>。行至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>，被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七日（时长）</span>不得食。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>的奇计，派人去贿赂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阏氏</span>，包<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span>才得以解开。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>既已脱险，其计谋很隐秘，世人都不知道。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "更封曲逆",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>南过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>，登上城头，望见屋舍甚多，说：\"这县真壮观！我走遍<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，只见<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>和这里如此。\"回头问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>户口多少？\"答：\"秦时有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万馀户</span>，近年战乱频繁，多逃亡隐匿，现有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千户</span>。\"于是下诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>，改封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">曲逆侯</span>，把全县作为他的食邑，免去先前所<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">户牖</span>乡。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "六出奇计",
      "text": "此后经常以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>身份随军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>。共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六</span>出奇计，每次都加增食邑，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六</span>次增封。这些奇计有的十分隐秘，世人无法得知。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "囚哙代将",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>从击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>军归来，箭伤复发，慢慢走到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，皇上派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>身份率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>刚走，有人进谗言中伤他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>发怒说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>见我病重，就巴望我死啊。\"采用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>的计策，召来<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周勃</span>在床下接受诏令，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>赶快驾<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">传</span>车载<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>地代替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>到军中立即<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>头！\"<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>领命后，乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">传</span>车，未到军中，商量说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>是皇帝的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">故人</span>，功劳多，又是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫</span>君，有亲又尊贵，皇上因一时愤怒，要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>他，恐怕事后会后悔。不如把他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>起来送交皇上，让皇上自己<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀他。\"未到军中，筑了<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">坛</span>，拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>召来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>接诏，立即被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反绑</span>装上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">囚车</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">传</span>送到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，而让绛<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>代为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>，率兵平〖[定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>乱的各县。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "避祸自全",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>在途中得知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>怕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>进谗言发怒，就赶快乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">传</span>车先行到长安。遇到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>传诏让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌婴</span>屯兵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>接诏后，立即驰入宫中，哭得很哀痛，乘势在丧前奏事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>同情他，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>辛苦了，出去休息吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>怕谗言得逞，坚决请求留下宿卫宫中。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>就任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中令</span>，说：\"辅佐教导<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉惠帝\">孝惠（汉惠帝）</span>。\"此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>的谗言不再得行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>押到，则<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免，恢复爵邑。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "王陵右相",
      "text": "孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>去世，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安国侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>为右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>为左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "王陵母节",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>，原是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人，起初是县里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪</span>强，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>微时，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>当<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>长事奉。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>少文化，任性气，好直言。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>也自己聚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">党</span>数千人，居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，不肯跟随沛公。等到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>才以兵归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>[取了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲放在军中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者到时，项羽就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>面朝东坐，想以此招降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>私下送走<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>，哭着说：\"替<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">老妾</span>告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>，好好侍奉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>是个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，不要因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">老妾</span>的缘故而怀二心。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妾</span>以死来送<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>。\"于是伏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>自尽。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>大怒，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span>煮了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>最终跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>平〖[定〖_天下</span>。因他与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>交好，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>又是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>的仇人，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>本无意跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>，所以较晚才封侯，为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安国侯</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "王陵忤吕",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安国侯</span>任右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二岁（时长）</span>，孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠帝</span>去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>想立诸吕为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>说：\"不可。\"问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"可。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>大怒，就假装升<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>为皇帝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>，实际不用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>发怒，告病辞官，闭门不朝见，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>后去世。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "徙平为右相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>调为右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辟阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">审食其</span>为左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>不理政事，常在宫中办事。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "审食其",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">食其</span>也是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>西被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打败</span>时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>作人质，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">食其</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>身份侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>。后来又随军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>所宠信。等到做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，在宫中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百官</span>都通过他决断事务。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "陈平韬晦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>常因先前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>出谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">捉</span>拿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>的事，屡次进谗言说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>不管事，每日饮醇<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>，戏弄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇女</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>听说后，变本加厉。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>听说，私下窃喜。当面对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>数落<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>说：\"俗话说'小孩子和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>的话不可信'，就看<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>和我关系如何罢了。不要怕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嬃</span>的谗言。\""
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "诛吕立文帝",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>立诸吕为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>假意顺从。及至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>合谋，终于<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭诸吕，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>是主谋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">审食其</span>被免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "平让勃右相",
      "text": "孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>立，认为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>亲自带兵<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>，功劳更大；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>想把尊位让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>，就称病。孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>初立，奇怪<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>病，问他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>功劳不如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>。但到<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭诸吕时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>功劳也不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>。愿把右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>。\"于是孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>就任命绛<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，位次第一；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>改任左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，位次第二。赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span>，增封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千户</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "问决狱钱谷",
      "text": "过了一段时间，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>对国家事务更加熟悉，一次上朝问右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>一年判决多少案件？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>道歉说：\"不知道。\"又问：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>一年<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>粮收支多少？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>又道歉说不知，汗流浃背，惭愧不能作答。于是皇上又问左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"有主管的人。\"皇上问：\"主管的是谁？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>要问决狱，请问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>；要问<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>粮，请问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">治粟内史</span>。\"皇上问：\"既然各有主管，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主管什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>道歉说：\"请陛下不要责备<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>不嫌<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愚钝，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰相</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰相</span>的职责，对上辅佐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>调理<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">阴阳</span>，顺<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四时</span>之气，对下养育万物使各得其宜，对外镇抚<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">四夷</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，对内亲附<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，使卿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>各司其职。\"孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>称善。右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>大为惭愧，出朝后责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>怎么不平时教我如何应对！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>笑道：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>居此位，不知所司之事吗？况且若<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>问<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">盗贼</span>数目，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>也要勉强回答吗？\"于是绛<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>自知才能远不及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>。过了一段时间，绛<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>称病请求免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>独任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "陈平卒后世",
      "text": "孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>去世，谥为献<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">共侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈买\">买（陈买）</span>继<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>侯位。过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">简侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈恢\">恢（陈恢）</span>继位。过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈何\">何（陈何）</span>继位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈何\">何（陈何）</span>因强<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夺他人之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>，被〖[弃市，国〖[除</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "阴谋自警",
      "text": "当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说过：\"我多设阴谋，这是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">道家</span>所忌讳的。我的家世要是衰废，也就罢了，终究不能复〖[起，因为我多有阴险之祸。\"但后来他的曾孙<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈掌</span>依附<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">卫氏</span>外戚而显贵，想请求续封<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陈氏</span>，但终未获准。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：陈<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>少年时，本好<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>的学说。当他在俎上分<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>时，其志向已很远大。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之间颠沛流离，最终归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>。常出奇计，救纷扰之难，解国家之忧。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>时，事多变故，然<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>最终自脱，安定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>，以荣名善终，被称为贤相，岂不是善始善终吗！不是有智谋的人谁能做到呢？"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>陋巷，门多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>。 分<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>先均，助丧后退。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>更易，腹心难托。 弃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>封<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，刺<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>露体。 间行归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，投身帐下。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>计全，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span>解。 推<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>，损多益寡。 应变合权，克〖[定宗社。"
    }
  }
}